com.snakk.advertising
Interface SnakkInterstitialAd.SnakkInterstitialAdListener

Enclosing interface:
SnakkInterstitialAd
public static interface SnakkInterstitialAd.SnakkInterstitialAdListener

Implement this interface to be notified of interstitial ad lifecycle changes.
